Package: MetaFeatures
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2014-05-05
Title: A package to produce Metafeature plots
Author: Charles Joly Beauparlant <charles.joly-beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>, Fabien Claude Lamaze <fabien.lamaze.1@ulaval.ca>, Rawane Samb <rawane.samb.1@ulaval.ca>, Astrid-Louise Deschenes <Astrid-Louise.Deschenes@crchudequebec.ulaval.ca> and Arnaud Droit <arnaud.droit@crchuq.ulaval.ca>.
Author@R: c(person("Charles", "Joly Beauparlant", email="charles.joly-beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca"),
        person("Fabien", "Claude Lamaze", email="fabien.lamaze.1@ulaval.ca"),
        person("Rawane", "Samb", email="rawane.samb.1@ulaval.ca"),
